Resler Says U.S. Economy `Not as Gloomy' as Some Say

-- B y  
-- 
2011-09-29T18:55:51Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-29/resler-says-u-s-economy-not-as-gloomy-as-some-say-video.html
David Resler, chief economic 
adviser at Nomura Securities International, talks about the U.S.
economy.  The economy grew at a 1.3 percent pace in the second 
quarter, faster than estimated last month. Resler also discusses
the U.S. labor market, stocks and Greece's sovereign debt 
crisis. He speaks with Mark Crumpton on Bloomberg Television's 
"Bottom Line." (Source: Bloomberg)  Running time 06:27
 